name: Dare to calm your self (Tributefortribute Aloysiusnitia)
description:
Dare to calm yourself, A dog is the only thing on earth that loves you more than you love yourself - Josh Billings

Mika and Pika tribute for Aloysiusnitia ( https://twitter.com/AloysiusNitia )
Mika is Pomeranian and Pika is Chihuahua.  
Mika is the one friendly and Pika is the spoiled one, I hope Mika and Pika are always healthy and happy, and always give love and full support to Aloy.

Aloy and Family and Pika and Mika are always live happily together
